    "## 3. Reconstruct dates and load weather data\n",
    "\n",
    "The cleaned Beam files contain engineered calendar fields such as `pickup_day`, `pickup_month`, and `pickup_hour`.  \n",
    "To merge with weather, we reconstruct a full `pickup_date`.\n",
    "\n",
    "Then we download daily weather for NYC using **Meteostat**.\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 3.1 Reconstruct pickup dates\n",
    "Create a stable calendar date from `pickup_day` + known month."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "pickup_date columns ready: jan mar may\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "from datetime import datetime\n",
    "\n",
    "def ensure_pickup_date(df: pd.DataFrame, month_value: int) -> pd.DataFrame:\n",
    "    if \"pickup_date\" not in df.columns:\n",
    "        day = pd.to_numeric(df[\"pickup_day\"], errors=\"coerce\").astype(\"Int64\")\n",
    "        ymd = (2020 * 10000 + month_value * 100) + day\n",
    "        df = df.copy()\n",
    "        df[\"pickup_date\"] = pd.to_datetime(ymd.astype(\"string\"), format=\"%Y%m%d\", errors=\"coerce\")\n",
    "    return df\n",
    "\n",
    "jan = ensure_pickup_date(jan, 1)\n",
    "mar = ensure_pickup_date(mar, 3)\n",
    "may = ensure_pickup_date(may, 5)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"pickup_date columns ready:\",\n",
    "      \"jan\" if \"pickup_date\" in jan.columns else \"jan-MISSING\",\n",
    "      \"mar\" if \"pickup_date\" in mar.columns else \"mar-MISSING\",\n",
    "      \"may\" if \"pickup_date\" in may.columns else \"may-MISSING\")"
   ]
  },
