    "### 6.1 Define TensorFlow model builders\n",
    "Create Linear, MLP, and DNN architectures required by the project prompt."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "#### 6.1.1 Linear regression baseline (Keras Sequential, no hidden layers)\n",
    "This is the assignment-required linear baseline for comparison against deeper models."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 26,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def build_linear_model(input_dim: int) -> keras.Model:\n",
    "    model = Sequential([\n",
    "        layers.Input(shape=(input_dim,)),\n",
    "        layers.Dense(1)\n",
    "    ], name=\"Linear_Regression\")\n",
    "    return model"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "#### 6.1.2 MLP model (compact non-linear baseline)\n",
    "Two hidden layers with dropout for regularized regression learning."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 27,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def build_mlp_model(input_dim: int) -> keras.Model:\n",
    "    model = Sequential([\n",
    "        layers.Input(shape=(input_dim,)),\n",
    "        layers.Dense(128, activation=\"relu\"),\n",
    "        layers.Dropout(0.20),\n",
    "        layers.Dense(64, activation=\"relu\"),\n",
    "        layers.Dropout(0.20),\n",
    "        layers.Dense(1)\n",
    "    ], name=\"MLP\")\n",
    "    return model"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "#### 6.1.3 DNN model (deeper architecture) and builder registry\n",
    "Four hidden layers with dropout; model registry lets us train all architectures in a loop."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 28,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def build_dnn_model(input_dim: int) -> keras.Model:\n",
    "    model = Sequential([\n",
    "        layers.Input(shape=(input_dim,)),\n",
    "        layers.Dense(256, activation=\"relu\"),\n",
    "        layers.Dropout(0.30),\n",
    "        layers.Dense(128, activation=\"relu\"),\n",
    "        layers.Dropout(0.30),\n",
    "        layers.Dense(64, activation=\"relu\"),\n",
    "        layers.Dropout(0.20),\n",
    "        layers.Dense(32, activation=\"relu\"),\n",
    "        layers.Dropout(0.20),\n",
    "        layers.Dense(1)\n",
    "    ], name=\"DNN\")\n",
    "    return model\n",
    "\n",
    "MODEL_BUILDERS = {\n",
    "    \"Linear\": build_linear_model,\n",
    "    \"MLP\": build_mlp_model,\n",
    "    \"DNN\": build_dnn_model,\n",
    "}"
